'''LkCa 15'''是一顆位於{{link-en|金牛座分子雲1|Taurus Molecular Cloud 1|金牛－御夫恆星形成區}}的恆[[金牛T星|金牛T星]]。該恆星是年輕的[[主序前星|主序前星]]，並且亮度變化不規則<ref name=dd>{{cite web|url=http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/T/TTauri.html|title=Encyclopedia of Science: T Tauri star|accessdate=17 January 2017|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127063304/https://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/T/TTauri.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 概要 ==
LkCa 15的質量大約是太陽的97%<ref name=EU/>，表面[[有效溫度|有效溫度]]是稍低於太陽的4370 K<ref name=temp>{{Cite journal|last=Thalmann, C. et al.|first=|date=1 June 2014|title=The architecture of the LkCa 15 transitional disk revealed by high-contrast imaging|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2014A%26A...566A..51T|journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics|volume=566|issue=id.A51|doi=|pmid=|access-date=|via=|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510132425/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2014A%26A...566A..51T|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它的[[視星等|視星等]]是肉眼不可見的11.91<ref name=EU/>。

LkCa 15和許多典型金牛T星一樣，周圍有[[原行星盤|原行星盤]]存在<ref name=dd/>。盤內物質的質量大約是太陽的0.5%<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Andrews & Williams|first=|date=8 June 2005|title=Circumstellar Dust Disks in Taurus-Auriga: The Submillimeter Perspective|url=http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/432712/meta|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=631|issue=2|doi=|pmid=|accessdate=11 September 2016|via=|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510121138/http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/432712/meta|dead-url=no}}</ref>。天文學家觀測到原行星盤的亮度有微小的變化，可能是盤內的[[原行星|原行星]]或行星所導致，並且目前已知該恆星旁有一顆系外行星[[LkCa_15_b|LkCa 15 b]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kraus & Ireland|first=|date=2012|title=A young exoplanet caught at formation?|url=|journal=Astrophysical Journal|volume=745|issue=|doi=|pmid=|access-date=|via=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Sallum S., et al.|first=|date=1 November 2015|title=Accreting Protoplanets in the LkCa15 transition disk|url=https://arxiv.org/abs/1511.07456|journal=Nature|volume=527|issue=|doi=|pmid=|access-date=|via=|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128183834/https://arxiv.org/abs/1511.07456|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這個名稱來自更早之前的一次巡天觀測<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Herbig et al.|first=|date=1 March 1986|title=A spectroscopic survey of the Taurus-Auriga dark clouds for pre-main-sequence stars having CA II H, K emission|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1986AJ.....91..575H|journal=The Astronomical Journal|volume=91|issue=|doi=|pmid=|access-date=11 September 2016|via=|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510133509/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1986AJ.....91..575H|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

